name: Anna Miller's
description:
最盛期には関東に20店舗も展開されていたのですが、先日、惜しまれつつも高輪店が閉店してしまいました。美味しいパイを出す制服がかわいいレストラン。その思い出をイラストで再現しようというLoRAです。

※CIVITAIのCategoryはBackgroundとしましたが、このLoRAでは制服（Clothing)・背景(background/scenery)・食品（Food,item)を学習させています。どうも複数カテゴリは設定できない模様


■制服：Costume / Trigger: AMSC

prompt (Orange Version)
AMSC, waitress, 1girl, indoors, solo, restaurant, black hair, window, holding, menu, uniform, standing, orange skirt, orange apron, full body, short sleeves, wooden table,

prompt (Pink Version)
AMSC, waitress, 1girl, indoors, solo, restaurant, black hair, window, holding, menu, uniform, standing, pink apron, pink skirt, ponytail, full body, short sleeves, wooden table,

制服の色はスカートとエプロンの色で指定してください。
Prompt skirt and apron related color specifications will change the color of the uniform

  • pink skirt, pink apron

  • orange skirt, orange apron

  • red skirt, red apron


■店内風景：Scenery inside the store / Trigger: AMTS （Anna Miller's高輪店）
AMTS, AMSC, 1girl, solo, realistic, pantyhose, brown hair, food, waitress, menu, smile, orange skirt, orange apron, uniform, looking at viewer, indoors, restaurant, shop, tile floor,

■お店外観・入り口：Entrance to the store / Trigger: AMTS
AMTS, scenery, restaurant, exterior, outdoors, realistic, photo background, photo (medium), photorealistic

■MENU
コーヒー・コーヒーカップ・ソーサー：Coffee
AMTS, cup, coffee, mug, saucer, coffee mug, still life, wooden table,

アップルパイ：ApplePie
applepie, plate, AMTS, cake, still life, food focus, food, wooden table,

ダッチアップルパイ　DUTCH APPLE PIE
dapie, plate, AMTS, cake, still life, food focus, food, wooden table,

バナナチョコパイ　BANANA CHOCOLATE PIE
bananachocopie, plate, AMTS, cake, still life, food focus, food, wooden table,

バナナパイ　BANANA PIE

bananapie, AMTS, plate, food focus, food, still life, cake, pastry, wooden table,

チェリーパイ　CHERRY PIE

cherrypie, AMTS, plate, food focus, food, still life, cake, wooden table,

フルーツクリームパイ　FRUITS CREAM PIE
fruitcreampie, plate, AMTS, cake, still life, food focus, food, strawberry,wooden table,

レモンパイ　LEMON PIE
lemonpie, AMTS, plate, food focus, food, still life, cake, wooden table,

パンケーキ　PANCAKE
AMTS, pancake, milk pitcher, cocotte, butter, plate, food focus, food, steam, still life, wooden table,
